node.title: Heavy rain warning issued for Fiordland
node.description: Between 80 to 100 millimetres of rain is expected to fall between this afternoon and tomorrow morning.
node.content:
["MetService has issued an orange rain warning for Fiordland.", "", "
\nPhoto: Unsplash / Erik Witsoe\n
", "It says between 80 to 100 millimetres of rain is expected to fall between this afternoon and tomorrow morning.", "That could cause surface flooding and slips and make driving conditions dangerous.", "MetService advise people to keep up to date with the latest forecasts, in case any changes are made or further areas are added."]
